		<title>英國經濟調高後，英鎊兌美元面臨關鍵考驗</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/gbpusd-major-test-uk-economic-boost</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[GBPUSD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新聞]]></category>
